(1, 'CN', 'The grandson saw that his grandfather had been single for a long time, so he took a wife less than 30 years old for him.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/smile.jpg', '0', '0', 55, '1', '1', 2, '0', 'Grandfather married a wife less than 30 years old.'),
(2, 'CN', 'Seeing that the grandfather liked the neighbor\'s grandmother but did not dare to confess, the grandchild pushed the boat to help him, who expected the neighbor\'s grandmother to like his grandchild.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/sk3.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'Grandpa likes the neighbor\'s grandmother, the neighbor\'s grandmother likes his grandson.'),
(3, 'CN', 'Hearing the good news from his son, he was deaf when he was about to have a grandchild, he lost his hearing so his wife was pregnant while the two of them had not slept together for 3 years.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/sk3.1.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/sk3.1.png', '0', 45, '3', '3', 2, '0', 'The couple\'s son announced the good news, the old man was deaf, thinking his wife was pregnant.'),
(4, 'CN', 'When her son informed her that she was about to become a grandmother, she was so happy that she forgot to put on makeup. When she looked in the mirror, she saw that she had distorted her eyes, lips, and hair, making her husband unrecognizable.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/co_chau.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/co_chau.png', '0', 50, '0', '1', 1, '0', 'When her son informed her that she was about to become a grandmother, she was so happy that she put on makeup that her husband did not recognize her.'),
(5, 'CN', 'When she learned that her daughter was about to have a grandchild, she was so happy that she forgot to call. When she looked back, she found that she had dialed the wrong number and talked to a stranger for ten minutes.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/dt.jpg', '0', '0', 60, '0', '1', 1, '0', 'When she was about to have a grandchild, she was so happy that she didn\'t know she was talking to a stranger for more than ten minutes.'),
(6, 'CN', 'When he heard that his son was about to have a grandson, he was so happy that he forgot to watch TV. When he looked back, he saw that he had dialed the wrong channel and watched the ghost movie for an hour.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/chau_noi.jpg', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/chau_noi.jpg', 28, '1', '0', 1, '0', 'When he heard that he was about to have a grandchild, he was so happy that he turned to watching ghost movies at any time.'),
(7, 'CN', 'When she heard that her daughter was going to have a grandchild, she was so excited that she forgot to sew a shirt. When I looked down, I saw that I had sewn my husband\'s shirt wrong into my skirt.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/chau.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/chau.jpg', '0', 45, '0', '1', 1, '0', 'She mistakenly sewed her husband\'s shirt into her skirt when she heard that she was going to have a grandchild.'),
(8, 'CN', 'When she was cutting her husband\'s hair, her son announced the good news that she was about to be promoted, she was so excited that she lost her husband\'s head.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/hair.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/hairnu.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/hair_nam.jpg', 30, '1', '1', 1, '0', 'She lost her husband\'s head when she heard that she was going to have a grandchild.'),
(9, 'CN', 'Walking on the street, his daughter-in-law called to tell him the good news that he was about to become a grandfather, he was so happy that he speeded up the car and ended up with all his teeth.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/vnmec.jpg', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/vnmec.jpg', 70, '2', '0', 1, '0', 'he lost his teeth when he found out he had a grandchild.'),
(10, 'CN', 'Son gives good news to grandparents who are about to be promoted, but do not know that the child is the product of his wife and father', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/grandfather.jpg', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/grandfather.jpg', 65, '1', '0', 1, '0', 'The son does not know that his child is a combination of his father and his wife.'),
(11, 'CN', 'When he heard that he was going to have a grandchild, he was so happy that he forgot to send an email. When I looked back at my computer, I saw that I had sent the wrong email to my boss and wrote: I love you, I want to marry you.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/ab35eee5c998d58a6d5d375be6dd6d311708c4ec/chau.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'He sent the wrong email to his boss and wrote: I love you, I want to marry you., when he heard that he was about to have a grandchild.'),
(12, 'CN', 'Knowing that she was about to become a grandmother, she rushed to her son\'s house, but went to the wrong house and slept with her son\'s neighbor.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/heli.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/heli.jpg', '0', 30, '1', '1', 2, '0', 'She slept with her son\'s neighbor when she learned she was about to become a grandmother.'),
(13, 'CN', 'Knowing that they were going to have a grandchild, the grandparents sold their house in the city to live with their son, but only after selling the house did they realize that the two children had tricked them into buying that house of theirs.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/house.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'When they heard that they were going to have a grandchild, they sold their house to go back to their hometown to take care of their grandchildren, but the news was fake.'),
(14, 'CN', 'When she heard that her son was about to have a grandchild, she was so happy that she forgot she was participating in a cooking competition. When she remembered, she was disqualified from the contest for not submitting her dish in time.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/cook.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'She was eliminated from the cooking competition after hearing that she was about to have a grandchild.'),
(15, 'CN', 'He was shocked when his grandson belonged to his son and ex-girlfriend.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/su.avif', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/su.avif', 50, '1', '0', 1, '0', 'He was not happy when he heard that his grandson was the son of his son and his ex-girlfriend.'),
(16, 'CN', 'Visiting her newborn grandchild, her mother-in-law held her grandchild and was peed on her hand.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/cild.png', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'Visiting her newborn grandchild, her mother-in-law held her grandchild and was peed on her hand.'),
(17, 'CN', 'She had not brushed her teeth for 3 years and heard her son announce that she was about to become a grandmother, she was so happy she kissed her husband on the lips and he died instantly because her mouth was too rotten.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/kiss.jpg', '0', '0', 70, '2', '2', 0, '0', 'After hearing that she was about to have a grandson, she kissed her husband on the lips, he died angry because his mouth was so dirty.'),
(18, 'CN', 'Seeing that the neighbor\'s grandparents were promoted to grandparents, the elderly couple decided to kidnap their grandchildren so that they could also be promoted to the same position as them.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/hiking.jpg', '0', '0', 60, '1', '0', 0, '0', 'The two grandparents made a bold decision to kidnap a neighbor\'s grandchild to become a grandparent like them.'),
(19, 'CN', 'When she heard that her son was about to have a grandson, she was so happy that she forgot she was teaching. When I remembered, I had a class, but the principal called me to notify me of my dismissal.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/45c73ba005a42ecd00a688ac7912cbda52e743ef/ba_noi.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'She was fired from her job after hearing that her grandson was so happy that she forgot to teach.'),
(20, 'CN', 'She was shocked when she heard that her son without a girlfriend announced that he was going to have a grandchild.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/tenahisicoates.jpg', '0', '0', 40, '4', '0', 1, '0', 'She was shocked when her son announced that he was going to have a grandchild.'),
(21, 'CN', 'She was shocked when her son got her boyfriend\'s daughter pregnant.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/bb_1.jpg', '0', '0', 30, '1', '1', 0, '0', 'She was shocked when her son got her boyfriend\'s daughter pregnant.'),
(22, 'CN', 'An old couple fought with a split forehead just because they wanted their daughter-in-law to have a daughter.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/86907a12cfdb37a0b1403e0a8feaf61145a7bf38/gia.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'Grandparents fight because they want their daughter-in-law to have a daughter.'),
(23, 'CN', 'Hearing the news that their son was about to become a grandparent, the two happily went to show it to everyone in the village, but when they returned home, they remembered that their lover was also a boy, how did they have children?', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/end.jpg', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/end.jpg', 30, '1', '0', 1, '0', 'Grandparents were shocked when they heard that they were going to have a grandchild, but the person who loved it was also a boy, how could they have children?'),
