(1, 'NYM', 'One week after breaking up, at her wedding, you caught a glimpse of her older sister. And both of you fell in love after that wedding.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ducmanhnguyen1308/-nh-cho-future-love/main/saostar-le6fhlsuzpwzbgwf.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/cutimage/main/nnu1.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/cutimage/main/nnam1.png', 27, '1', '1', 2, '0', 'His new lover is his ex-girlfriend\'s older sister.'),
(2, 'NYM', 'What will you be like after 3 years of breaking up? Will you have to get back with your ex because you couldn\'t pay off all your debts to them?', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/293cee056821d6bd1973558c958211490e48a29a/N-Y-M.jpg', '0', '0', 27, '5', '5', 0, '0', 'Your new lover is your ex-girlfriend because you haven\'t paid them off in full.'),
