(4, 'NYM', 'The wife discovered that her husband had proposed to break up with his ex-girlfriend because her family was too poor. He had fallen in love with his wife because of material possessions.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ducmanhnguyen1308/-nh-cho-future-love/main/chia-tay-ban-gai-doi-300-trieu-tien-phi-qua-3-nam-toi-bat-khoc-nhin-nguoi-ben-canh-em-1_248726-1623952986-194-width640height480.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ducmanhnguyen1308/-nh-cho-future-love/main/chia-tay-ban-gai-doi-300-trieu-tien-phi-qua-3-nam-toi-bat-khoc-nhin-nguoi-ben-canh-em-1_248726-1623952986-194-width640height480.jpg', '0', 30, '', '2', 1, '0', 'Your new lover is a materialistic husband.'),
(5, 'NYM', 'At the age of 35, the husband and wife will reunite and proceed to marriage.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/futurelove/main/nym1.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/cutimage/main/nym2nu.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/cutimage/main/nym1nam.png', 35, '2', '2', 2, 'namtruoc', 'You will meet your new lover at the age of 35 and the two will move towards marriage.'),
(6, 'NYM', 'At the age of 40, the wife returned to her husband because at that time he was a wealthy heir.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ducmanhnguyen1308/-nh-cho-future-love/main/happy-wife-welcoming-her-military-husband-after-returning-back-home-from-army_116547-17523.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ducmanhnguyen1308/-nh-cho-future-love/main/happy-wife-welcoming-her-military-husband-after-returning-back-home-from-army_116547-17523.jpg', '0', 40, '', '3', 1, '0', 'At 40 years old, his new lover is his ex-wife'),
(7, 'NYM', 'After the breakup, the husband returned to his ex-girlfriend because she was more beautiful than his wife.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/bae6a364b3cd0bd0e22b28b66cbb0f2a72858915/girlfriend.png', '0', '0', 30, '5', '5', 0, '0', 'Your husband\'s new lover is his ex-girlfriend.'),
(8, 'NYM', 'At 50 years old, how will the two of you be? The husband already has a new girlfriend, who is a famous singer.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/futurelove/main/ct11.jpg', '0', '0', 50, '1', '0', 1, '0', 'At 50 years old, your new lover is a famous singer.'),
(9, 'NYM', 'At 30 years old, who will be in your family? The family consists of 7 people: the husband, the wife, and 5 children.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/c5ce2790419080e97db4df33adc797a0f42c417e/Gia_dinh.jpg', '0', '0', 30, '5', '5', 0, '0', 'At 30 years old, who will be in your family? The family consists of 7 people: the husband, the wife, and 5 children.'),
(10, 'NYM', 'After the husband and wife broke up, the husband fell in love with his  best friend and they got married. After a year, they broke up because the husband realized he still loved his ex-wife.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/futurelove/main/nym3.jpg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/cutimage/main/nym3nu.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thuykieu06012002/cutimage/main/nym3nam.png', 40, '4', '4', 2, 'namtruoc', 'Your husband\'s new lover is the friend after the previous breakup.'),
(11, 'NYM', 'After breaking up, the husband discovered that he was the third sex. Husband and husband\'s best friend fell in love', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ducmanhnguyen1308/-nh-cho-future-love/main/dong-tinh-luyen-ai-do-dau11453804634.jpg', '0', '0', 45, '1', '0', 1, '0', 'Your husband\'s new lover is his best friend.'),
(12, 'NYM', 'One week after breaking up with his wife, the husband started dating his teacher who is 20 years older than him.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym_nu.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym_nam.png', 40, '1', '1', 0, '0', 'Your husband\'s new lover is a teacher 20 years older than you.'),
(13, 'NYM', 'After 2 weeks of breaking up, the wife was proposed by the husband\'s older brother. The wife and the older brother got married and lived together under the same roof.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym1.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym1_nu.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym1_nam.png', 35, '1', '1', 0, 'namtruoc', 'Your wife\'s new lover is your brother and they are married.'),
(14, 'NYM', 'The beauty of the ex-boyfriend\'s new girlfriend is so bad, that beauty is not even half half of her.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/myn.jpg', '0', '0', 25, '0', '2', 1, '0', 'The beauty of your new lover is worse than her Thi bloom in the story of chi Pheo.'),
(15, 'NYM', 'You suddenly realize your new lover is your ex\'s best friend and they have known each other for a long time.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/myn1.jpg', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/myn1.jpg', 30, '1', '1', 1, '0', 'You suddenly realize your new lover is your ex\'s best friend and they have known each other for a long time.'),
(16, 'NYM', 'You and your new lover go shopping at the supermarket. You, unfortunately, lost your wallet and do not have the money to pay for the goods. Your new lover says they will pay you but when they go to the cashier they run away.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/myn2.jpg', '0', '0', 27, '2', '0', 0, '0', 'You go to buy things but lost your wallet, your new lover says they will pay you but when they get to the cashier, they run away.'),
(17, 'NYM', 'You and your new lover go to eat ice cream at a famous ice cream shop. Little did you know that your new lover is a huge fan of a famous singer and they met their idol at that ice cream parlor. Your new lover has left you behind to pursue that singer.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/060434b8ad6c27d2e1abf2ece021c2f24d4328d0/valentine-1.2.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'You and your new lover go to eat ice cream and meet a famous singer, Your new lover has abandoned you to pursue that singer.'),
(18, 'NYM', 'Introduced to her family by her new boyfriend, the stressed-out sweaty girl washed away her make-up, making her boyfriend not recognize her and mistakenly picking up her roommate.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym_1.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/nym_1.png', '0', 27, '0', '1', 1, '0', 'The girl was brought home by her boyfriend to debut with her family, the girl was nervous and sweaty to remove makeup, making her boyfriend not recognize and pick up the wrong roommate.'),
(19, 'NYM', 'You and your new lover go to a birthday party. You don\'t know that your new lover is a very sociable and funny person. At the party, your new lover has made friends with everyone and has kissed front of you with another girl.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/1.2.jpg', '0', '0', 35, '2', '2', 0, 'namsau', 'Your new lover is a jovial sociable, on his birthday he kissed a girl in front of you.'),
(20, 'NYM', 'She and her new lover go to a thrilling game. During the play, she feels normal and excited, and her lover screams, fearfully hugging her.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/1.3.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/1.3.png', '0', 30, '0', '4', 1, '0', 'Her new lover is a weak guy who is scared of thrilling games.'),
(21, 'NYM', 'You and your new lover go to eat pizza at a famous restaurant. Little did you know that your new crush is a huge fan of a K-pop group and they met their idol at that pizzeria. Your new lover has left you behind to run with that band and ask for autographs.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/6d174f328c9e21ea10aabaf206b0e8599c8b1900/an_toi.jpg', '0', '0', 0, '0', '0', 0, '0', 'You and your new lover go out to eat at a pizzeria. Your new crush left you behind to run after that band and get autographs.'),
