(23, 'NYM', 'The girl and her new lover had a date to go to the park. The girl wanted to commemorate the photos with her new lover and asked a passerby for help. Unexpectedly, the person being asked was his ex-girlfriend, he stole the phone and ran away.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/ae02276886372a3b84aef6bbefb7a99144108eb1/hen_ho.jpg', '0', '0', 30, '1', '0', 0, '0', 'The girl was robbed of her phone by an old friend while going to the park with her new boyfriend.'),
(24, 'NYM', 'The girl and her new boyfriend participated in an intelligence contest on television and had to answer a question related to her ex-lover, everyone around her thought of letting go of this question, but she insisted on answering for her. By all means, she spent a whole day telling all the information about her ex-lover, causing her new boyfriend to lose face and leave her first.', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/main/1.5.png', '0', '0', 30, '3', '1', 1, 'namsau', 'The girl on television spent a whole day talking about her ex-lover, making her new boyfriend lose face and leaving the old story.'),
