(16, 'SC', 'The newly born and abandoned child is now the lover of her current biological daughter', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/c45738b3b28e16a7d6ae3155f9e2ce88cc06a61b/love_Banh_mi.jpg', '0', '0', 28, '1', '1', 0, 0, 'The first child was abandoned.'),
