(20, 'SC', 'The eldest son found out that his father molested his daughter-in-law', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/8f12d4033b13207e8bbd030cfddf5d32415c47bb/man.jpg', '0', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spiderdassness/anh_raw/8f12d4033b13207e8bbd030cfddf5d32415c47bb/man.jpg', 55, '1', NULL, 1, 0, 'The father-in-law had an affair with his sister-in-law.'),
